## How to build?

To make nonce static on HVS, change in host connector library â€“
host-connector/src/main/java/com/intel/mtwilson/core/host/connector/intel/TAHelper.java
237: +  nonce = Base64.decodeBase64("+c4ZEmco4aj1G5dTXQvjIMGFd44=");

To make TLS connection possible to simulated hosts update HVS,
features/mtwilson-flavor-ws-v2/src/main/java/com/intel/mtwilson/flavor/rest/v2/resource/HostResource.java
596: -            return createTlsPolicy(tlsPolicyIdentifier, hostId);
     +            return createTlsPolicy(tlsPolicyIdentifier, null);

Copy updated jars manually to ./share. Run ./build.sh to generate build.

## How to deploy??
Pre-requisites for starting server on some other system:
# yum install -y python python-pip python-wheel

In case, pip is not present in repository use -
# wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
# python get-pip.py

# pip install flask flask_basicauth
# pip install jprops

Generate self-signed certificate:
# openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -nodes -out cert.pem -keyout key.pem -days 365

Start service:
# ./tagent-sim.sh start

Create host:
# ./tagent-sim.sh create-all-hosts

Create host:
# ./tagent-sim.sh create-all-flavors

Start service:
# ./tagent-sim.sh stop

Help on all services:
# ./tagent-sim.sh help

Check log
# vi simulator.log

Access service:
# curl https://127.0.0.1:10000/quote -k -u admin:admin

Remove proxy in case curl fails
# export https_proxy=
# export http_proxy=

Pending Tasks:
1. Adding asset tag 
2. Performance measurement


